<H5 class=3D"posthead pageTitle">Happy News for Open XML Developers =
</H5>
<P>Many of you may have already heard that <A=20
href=3D"http://www.microsoft.com/presspass/press/2008/apr08/04-01OpenXMLV=
otePR.mspx"=20
target=3D_blank=20
mce_href=3D"http://www.microsoft.com/presspass/press/2008/apr08/04-01Open=
XMLVotePR.mspx">Office=20
Open XML was approved as an ISO standard</A>! This is great news for all =
of us=20
who have been developing solutions using Open XML. You can find all the =
details=20
in <A=20
href=3D"http://blogs.msdn.com/brian_jones/archive/2008/04/01/open-xml-ove=
rwhelmingly-approved-as-an-iso-iec-standard-is-29500-the-end-of-the-file-=
formats-war.aspx"=20
target=3D_blank=20
