-overwhelmingly-approved-as-an-iso-iec-standard-is-29500-the-end-of-the-f=
ile-formats-war.aspx">Brian's=20
blog</A>. Also, <A=20
href=3D"http://blogs.msdn.com/dmahugh/archive/2008/04/01/is29500.aspx"=20
target=3D_blank=20
mce_href=3D"http://blogs.msdn.com/dmahugh/archive/2008/04/01/is29500.aspx=
">Doug=20
Mahugh provides great pointers</A> to other bloggers that talk about =
this.</P>
<H3>Getting Started with Open XML Development</H3>
